You can now watch South Africa play Ghana tonight, after the Confederation of African Football supplied a live stream link to the match. Football fans can finally watch the Bafana v Ghana 2021 Africa Cup of Nations qualifier, via live stream. The Bafana Bafana twitter account tweeted a livestream to the match. Here it is: https://lagarderelivesp1-lh.akamaihd.net/i/CAF_M5@378581/master.m3u8